STATE of North Carolina
v.
Eddie M. IVEY. No. 501P98-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2009. Eddie M. Ivey, Pro Se. John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General, L. Johnson Britt, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 11th day of December 2008 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Robeson County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2009."
